name: Classic Roblox 2017
description: A nostalgic throwback to the golden era of Roblox with authentic sounds and animations
author: RobloxNostalgic

instructions: 1. Install BetterDiscord if you haven't already
2. Place this theme file in your BetterDiscord themes folder
3. Enable the theme in BetterDiscord settings
4. Add your own Roblox logo base64 to the CSS where indicated
5. Replace the placeholder sound URLs with actual Roblox sound files
6. Enjoy your nostalgic Roblox Discord experience!
requirements: Modern web browser with audio support
notes: Sound effects are placeholder base64 - replace with actual Roblox sounds
Logo placeholder provided - add your own 2012 Roblox logo
Theme optimized for classic 2017 Roblox aesthetic
All animations and effects are performance-optimized
